@startuml CommunicationDiagram
title Create Reservation - Communication Diagram (Clean)

object User
object Frontend
object Backend
object ReservationService
object SlotService
object Database

User --> Frontend : 1: select slot
Frontend --> Backend : 2: create reservation
Backend --> ReservationService : 3: createReservation()
ReservationService --> SlotService : 4: check slot
SlotService --> Database : 5: query
Database --> ReservationService : 6: result
ReservationService --> Database : 7: insert reservation
ReservationService --> Database : 8: update slot
Backend --> Frontend : 9: success
Frontend --> User : 10: confirmation

@enduml